Dancing with the Stars - Season 20, Episode 14




The Finals

It's all led to this as the Dancing with the Stars season 20 Finals begin with each of the three remaining couples performing two full routines. First, each couple repeated a dance from earlier in the season. Then, the couples pulled out all the stops for their supersized Freestyle performances featuring special effects, guest dancers, and even more big surprises!




Original Air Date: 18-May-2015
